<br>
I really expected more of a fight from him, was kind of disappointing or anti-climatic even.  Oh well, it's done at least now and I can move on to Sky and get my Fiery Avenger after all this time.<br>
<br>
Just two mid 50's group can take him easily or one full group of upper 50's can do him fine.<br>
<br>
